Package: Scissor
Version: 2.0.0
Title: Single-Cell Identification of Subpopulations with bulk Sample phenOtype coRrelation (SCISSOR)
Authors@R: c(person("Duanchen", "Sun", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "sund@ohsu.edu"))
Maintainer: Duanchen Sun <sund@ohsu.edu>
Description: Scissor is a novel approach that utilizes the bulk phenotypes, such as disease stage, tumor metastasis, treatment response, and survival outcomes, to identify the most highly phenotype-associated cell subpopulations from single-cell data.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: R (>= 3.6.1), Seurat (>= 3.2.0), Matrix (>= 1.2-18)
